wiki.summary: “WORST DAY” is a Valentine’s Day special single by the Atlanta native rapper, Future. This standalone release is his first solo single since his April 2020 track “Tycoon”. wiki.content: “WORST DAY” is a Valentine’s Day special single by the Atlanta native rapper, Future. This standalone release is his first solo single since his April 2020 track “Tycoon”. Future first announced the track via Instagram while previewing its official music video, which stars Kevin Samuels, a counselor and dating advisor who does many in-depth dating interviews on his official YouTube channel. The music video itself is presented as an interview, titled Healing Together, as shown in the official trailer that was posted the same day as the track’s first announcement. Read more on Last.fm.
